                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10153" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1164</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">187 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破界与创新：“水果女王”邓湘君的农业创业之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking Boundaries and Driving Innovation: The Agricultural Entrepreneurship Journey of &quot;Fruit Queen&quot; Deng Xiangjun</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">易朝辉，何嘉琪，梁佳欣，杨可</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南农业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南省禹佑农业综合开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字创业；女性创业者；身份构建；乡村振兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Digital Entrepreneurship; Female Entrepreneurs; Identity Construction; Rural Revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了邓湘君带领“禹佑农业综合开发有限公司”从传统农业向智慧农业转型升级，进而带动乡村产业振兴的创新实践过程。在乡村振兴战略背景下，从广铁集团辞职而后涉足互联网、心理教育、餐饮等行业的邓湘君，跨界投身农业，运用“一树一码”、“一果一证”溯源系统和农业大数据平台实现精准管理，率先自创了“高标准精细化智慧果园+模块化建园方案+标准化输出”的农业模式，同时通过果树认养、电商营销等多元渠道拓展市场，成功打造出集农业生产、科技示范、休闲观光于一体的现代智慧田园综合体示范基地。本案例旨在帮助学生了解女性创业者如何通过资源整合构建创业者身份，进而阐释其“反馈获取—反馈识别—机会迭代”的动态调整开发策略过程，解析价值共创的生态化发展逻辑，探讨数字平台赋能农业产业集群路径，为农业领域数字创业提供宝贵实践经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes how Deng Xiangjun led the &quot;Yu You Agricultural Comprehensive Development Co., Ltd.&quot; in its innovative transformation from traditional agriculture to smart agriculture, thereby driving rural industrial revitalization. Against the backdrop of the Rural Revitalization Strategy, Deng Xiangjun, who resigned from China Railway and later ventured into the internet, psychological education, and catering industries, crossed over into agriculture. She employed a traceability system with &quot;one code per tree&quot; and &quot;one certificate per fruit,&quot; as well as an agricultural big data platform, to achieve precise management. She was the first to create an agricultural model of &quot;high-standard and refined smart orchard, modular orchard construction plan, standardized output.&quot; Meanwhile, through diversified channels such as tree adoption and e-commerce marketing, she successfully developed a modern smart pastoral complex demonstration base that integrates agricultural production, technological demonstration, and leisure tourism. This case aims to help students understand how female entrepreneurs build their entrepreneurial identities through resource integration. It further explains the dynamic adjustment and development strategy process of &quot;feedback acquisition-feedback identification-opportunity iteration,&quot; analyzes the ecological logic of value co-creation, explores the path of digital platform empowerment for agricultural industry clusters, and provides valuable practical experience for digital entrepreneurship in the agricultural field.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2004</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">女性创业意图；女性数字创业支持因素；基于意义建构的机会开发过程；商业生态系统与价值共创；数字平台赋能农业可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
